Movement:

WASD keys

Picking up an item:

Shift + QWEASDZXC (directional)
  or
Drag from world to an inventory slot
  or
Drag from world to your player

Crafting:

1234567890 to select slot in inventory
  or
Ctrl + WASD to change selected slot
Space + QWEASDZXC to use selected slot
Alt + QWEASDZXC to use hand

Item Craft Selection:

Click
  or
WASD to change selection, space to confirm

Other:

Double click item in inventory to equip
Double click equipped item to unequip
Right click item in inventory to view recipe book
Q to drop a single item of currently selected slot
